{"tid":1725661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（核彈）警察企圖槍殺記者，開左一槍！","createTime":"2019-11-15T21:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:38:39.000Z","uid":248857,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc9f43ffeb002b52ff40de8c94f7b1293d54766","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:54:52.000Z","msg":"【旺角】有商台記者收工前往搭車時，目睹記者行家被防暴警推撞，警員呼喝「咩記者嚟？幫暴徒擋子彈」，並一直指記者襲警。商台記者於是上前拍攝保障行家權益，惟防暴警見狀即上前阻止拍攝，記者不就範繼續拍攝，隨即有警員大叫「拉佢！」。<br />\n<br />\n商台記者逃跑，其間警員舉起防暴槍向記者發射一發子彈，擊中背囊，幸無受傷。記者指不確定警方發射哪種子彈，但現場附近拾獲一粒海綿彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckwJ0ez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckwJ0ez.png&h=16079152&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cb62c68c571b505d9e503adbb194967f9cb7d98","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:56:13.000Z","msg":"Push 1/10"},{"pid":"e99ce9f7a94318d4029f9728722ee90562b845bc","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:56:33.000Z","msg":"Push 2/10"},{"pid":"a9633715c790258d48bc2753fb3c9325f9f37a54","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:56:49.000Z","msg":"Push 3/10"},{"pid":"5e6a77ec96be6cd65d4a3e074775d23bd28f8d32","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"Push 4/10"},{"pid":"57560fa10e082a50d5485ca7934326b907a284d0","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:57:32.000Z","msg":"Push 5/10"},{"pid":"3bab1ca1d1e477a505e0c54153c07f8b601fc368","tid":1725661,"uid":248857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:57:43.000Z","msg":"Push 6/10"},{"pid":"200fefa7ca7b6f57859d966a660ed24b55a38057","tid":1725661,"uid":312859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T21:57:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-si